CompetitionMetaData.Help:
This Competition implement the PixelFlut protocol: PX {x} {y} {r} {g} {b} - or - PX {x} {y} #{color}
x: x-Coordinate of a pixel y: y-Coordinate of a pixel r: red color component of a pixel g: green color component of a pixel b: blue color component of a pixel
color: color encoded as a html color (rgb-values as hex)
